---
title: Super Quick Thai Green Style Chicken Curry with Baby Spinach and Fragrant Jasmine Rice
description: Basil, coriander, makrut lime leaves and green chillies give Thai Green its signature colour, as well as its fragrant flavour. Our Super Quick Thai Green Style Chicken Curry will be on your table in less than 15 minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R07_W06_UK_UQ16100-5_Main_low-cede0aac.jpg
